Project details: 
Convo is an innovative AI tool designed to enhance online discourse. It analyzes posts across various platforms to identify key elements that encourage deep, meaningful dialogue. Its capabilities include evaluating draft posts to predict their potential for fostering in-depth conversations and offering suggestions for improvements or new prompts. Convo aims to reduce online polarization and promote understanding, empathy, and compromise, especially significant during an election year. This tool is vital for improving the quality and substance of online communication.
